      },
      "id": 14,
      "options": {
        "content": "**Two systems, one program.**\n\nThe **batch load pipeline** (One Fintech) receives RFU eligibility files (SRG310/315/320), translates them into FIS RT/AT batch commands, sends to FIS Prepaid Sunrise, and reconciles return files. Seven stages. ECS Fargate single container.\n\nThe **Universal Wallet** (UW) is the cardholder-facing app. It depends on the batch pipeline having issued the card before a member can add it.\n\n**Environments:** DEV \u00b7 TST \u00b7 PRD\n\n**Stack:** Go 1.25.8 \u00b7 Aurora PostgreSQL Serverless v2 \u00b7 AWS ECS Fargate \u00b7 EventBridge \u00b7 S3 \u00b7 CloudWatch \u2192 Datadog",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Architecture",
      "type": "text"
    },
